content:
Create assets to track products purchased by your customers.

Available in Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience, Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions.

USER PERMISSIONS NEEDED

To create assets: 

Create on assets

Click New on the Assets home page or on the Assets related list on a record.
Select a product.
Enter a name for the asset.
Select an account, contact, or both to indicate who has purchased the asset (required).
Optionally, select a parent asset.
Fill out the remaining fields according to your needs.
Save your changes.
